* 17 pwm channels are available on Colibri Vybrid50

Compile the driver source using the Make file in the driver source directory, copy the kernel object obtained (mvf-pwm.ko) to Colibri-VF50 board.

Import the Eclipse project of demo application and bild the project, copy the demo application (mvf-pwm-demo) to Colibri-VF50 board.

/* ON COLIBRI EVALUATION BOARD V3.1a */ 							
Load the kernel object using :
insmod mvf-pwm.ko

check the debug messages.

Run the mvf-pwm-demo application.

The demo application is just for controlling a serveo motor on one channel and an led on other channel.

